{
  "info": {
    "name": "BidMart API v2.0",
    "description": "Updated Postman collection sesuai dengan API Contract v2.0. JWT token otomatis tersimpan setelah login. Urutan testing: Auth → User → Wallet (top-up) → Listing (sebagai seller) → Bidding (sebagai buyer) → Notification → Order.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "version": "2.0.0"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "baseUrl", "value": "http://localhost:8080", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "token", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "refreshToken", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "tempToken", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "userId", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "sellerToken", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "sellerId", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "listingId", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "bidId", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "orderId", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "notificationId", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "sessionId", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "categoryId", "value": "", "type": "string" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "📖 README — Baca Dulu",
      "description": "Quickstart guide untuk test BidMart end-to-end.\n\n=== HAPPY PATH FLOW ===\n\n1. Auth → Register (buyer)\n2. Auth → Register (Seller)\n3. Auth → Login (buyer) → token otomatis tersimpan\n4. User → Get My Profile → userId tersimpan\n5. Wallet → Top Up (10jt)\n6. Auth → Login (Seller) → token seller tersimpan ke variable `sellerToken`\n7. Listing → Create Listing → listingId tersimpan\n8. Auth → Login (buyer) lagi → kembali ke buyer\n9. Bidding → Get Minimum Next Bid\n10. Bidding → Place Bid\n11. Notification → Get My Notifications → cek NEW_BID\n12. Wallet → Get Balance → cek balanceLocked\n13. Tunggu auction expire ATAU buat listing dengan endTime cepat\n14. Order → Get My Orders → cek order otomatis terbuat\n15. Notification → cek AUCTION_WON\n\n=== ANTI-SNIPING TEST ===\n1. Buat listing dengan endTime 1-2 menit dari sekarang\n2. Bid sebelum waktu habis\n3. Cek listing → endTime extend 2 menit + status EXTENDED\n\n=== OUTBID TEST ===\n1. Buyer A bid 5.5jt\n2. Login Buyer B → bid 6jt\n3. Cek notifikasi Buyer A → OUTBID muncul\n4. Cek balance Buyer A → hold di-release",
      "item": []
    },
    {
      "name": "🔐 Auth",
      "description": "Auth flow: Register → Login → (optional MFA) → get tokens. Token otomatis tersimpan.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Register (Buyer)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 201) {",
                  "    const res = pm.response.json();",
                  "    console.log('✅ Buyer registered. Sekarang login.');",
                  "    pm.test('Status 201', () => pm.response.to.have.status(201));",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"username\": \"buyer01\",\n  \"email\": \"buyer01@example.com\",\n  \"displayName\": \"Buyer Satu\",\n  \"password\": \"password123\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "auth", "register"]
            },
            "description": "Daftar akun buyer baru. Wallet otomatis dibuat via event listener — tidak perlu call /api/wallet/register."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Register (Seller)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"username\": \"seller01\",\n  \"email\": \"seller01@example.com\",\n  \"displayName\": \"Seller Satu\",\n  \"password\": \"password123\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "auth", "register"]
            },
            "description": "Register akun kandidat seller. Secara default backend register membuat role USER, jadi akun ini harus sudah dipromote/di-seed sebagai SELLER sebelum tokennya bisa dipakai untuk create listing."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Login (Buyer)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    const res = pm.response.json();",
                  "    if (res.mfaRequired) {",
                  "        pm.collectionVariables.set('tempToken', res.tempToken);",
                  "        console.log('⚠️ MFA required. Lanjut ke Verify MFA.');",
                  "    } else if (res.accessToken) {",
                  "        pm.collectionVariables.set('token', res.accessToken);",
                  "        pm.collectionVariables.set('refreshToken', res.refreshToken);",
                  "        console.log('✅ Login buyer berhasil. Token tersimpan.');",
                  "    }",
                  "    pm.test('Status 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"identifier\": \"buyer01\",\n  \"password\": \"password123\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "auth", "login"]
            },
            "description": "identifier bisa username atau email. Token JWT otomatis tersimpan ke {{token}}."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Login (Seller)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    const res = pm.response.json();",
                  "    if (res.accessToken) {",
                  "        pm.collectionVariables.set('sellerToken', res.accessToken);",
                  "        console.log('Login seller berhasil. Pastikan akun ini ber-role SELLER. Token tersimpan ke {{sellerToken}}.');",
                  "    }",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"identifier\": \"seller01\",\n  \"password\": \"password123\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "auth", "login"]
            },
            "description": "Login memakai akun yang sudah ber-role SELLER. Token disimpan ke {{sellerToken}} agar tidak overwrite buyer token."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Verify MFA",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    const res = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('token', res.accessToken);",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('refreshToken', res.refreshToken);",
                  "    console.log('✅ MFA verified. Token tersimpan.');",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"tempToken\": \"{{tempToken}}\",\n  \"code\": \"123456\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/verify-mfa",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "auth", "verify-mfa"]
            },
            "description": "Verify TOTP code (6 digit dari authenticator app). Gunakan tempToken dari response login MFA."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Refresh Token",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    const res = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('token', res.accessToken);",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('refreshToken', res.refreshToken);",
                  "    console.log('✅ Token diperbarui.');",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"refreshToken\": \"{{refreshToken}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/refresh",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "auth", "refresh"]
            },
            "description": "Gunakan refresh token (valid 7 hari) untuk dapat access token baru. Refresh token lama otomatis di-revoke."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Verify Email",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/verify?token=EMAIL_VERIFICATION_TOKEN_HERE",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "auth", "verify"],
              "query": [{ "key": "token", "value": "EMAIL_VERIFICATION_TOKEN_HERE" }]
            },
            "description": "Verifikasi email pakai token yang dikirim ke email user."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "👤 User Profile",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Get My Profile",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
